('1c9b30c0-ae63-4167-9cf6-06e333325c94',450923,'Why configuration is so complicated',replace('<p>Why can‚Äôt <a href="https://mark-burgess-oslo-mb.medium.com/why-cant-configuration-be-made-simple-16eb70ed5455">configuration be made simple</a>?¬†</p><p>Apple is making it easier for users to <a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/11/24127278/apple-iphone-repair-used-parts">repair their iPhones with used parts</a>.</p><p>Texas is <a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/10/24126206/texas-staar-exam-graders-ai-automated-scoring-engine">swapping human graders for AI</a>.</p><p>Automattic (owner of WordPress) is <a href="https://techcrunch.com/2024/04/09/wordpress-com-owner-automattic-acquires-multi-service-messaging-app-beeper-for-125m/?guccounter=1&guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8&guce_referrer_sig=AQAAAE4eQ0XLijDIe57gP_qJNDZrcXJLaeXVJnQWP02-MhexC86NMmKjstwTS8N_y04VD5GJUOb2oIiMx91gbGMpZ8odK31p3K0VM6glPk586DGFPj__CiV1a6QK7so1oVqxACufJ5uwu9X9RqcOhMZuJ-5yx7OwPu3jeWWn3Fgb_bzR">acquiring Beeper for $125M</a>.</p><p>Silicon Valley or not, San Francisco‚Äôs train system <a href="https://www.wired.com/story/san-francisco-muni-trains-floppy-disks/">still uses floppy disks</a>. But don‚Äôt worry, an upgrade is coming‚Äîin 2030.</p><p>Shoutout to <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/users/9951/bite-code">Bite code</a>, who earned a <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/help/badges/36/stellar-question">Stellar Question badge</a> with <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2432764/how-do-i-change-the-uri-url-for-a-remote-git-repository">How do I change the URI (URL) for a remote Git repository?</a>.</p>\n','\n',char(10)),'https://stackoverflow.blog/podcast/','https://chrt.fm/track/G8F1AF/pdrl.fm/c28362/injector.simplecastaudio.com/6fa1d34c-502b-4abf-bd82-483804006e0b/episodes/a23de6d6-005c-44cb-91ee-4fde30237654/audio/128/default.mp3?aid=rss_feed&awCollectionId=6fa1d34c-502b-4abf-bd82-483804006e0b&awEpisodeId=a23de6d6-005c-44cb-91ee-4fde30237654&feed=XA_851k3',171350