('014d3d8f-f368-4fdb-a3d1-cf15be40261e',450923,'If everyone is building AI, why aren''t more projects in production?',replace('<p>Get started with <a href="https://www.mongodb.com/mongodb-on-google-cloud">MongoDB Atlas on Google Cloud</a> today.¬†</p><p>Read more from the MongoDB DevRel team at <a href="https://www.mongodb.com/developer/">the MongoDB Developer Center</a>.</p><p>Learn more about Google‚Äôs <a href="https://ai.google.dev/models/gemini">Gemini models</a>.¬†</p><p>Shout out to <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/users/186836/thitemple">thitemple</a> for their <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/help/badges/8842/lifeboat">Lifeboat</a>-worthy answer to <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/41882174/in-typescript-how-do-i-declare-a-function-that-returns-a-string-type-array/41882274#41882274">In TypeScript, how do I declare a function that returns a string type array?</a>.</p>\n','\n',char(10)),'https://stackoverflow.blog/podcast/','https://chrt.fm/track/G8F1AF/pdrl.fm/c28362/injector.simplecastaudio.com/6fa1d34c-502b-4abf-bd82-483804006e0b/episodes/d0d08664-1aff-4f74-8107-475f389207d1/audio/128/default.mp3?aid=rss_feed&awCollectionId=6fa1d34c-502b-4abf-bd82-483804006e0b&awEpisodeId=d0d08664-1aff-4f74-8107-475f389207d1&feed=XA_851k3',1713327600,2498,0,693,0),
